{"tid":1812011,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[救十三億人] 發現咗疑似可以控制疫情嘅方法","createTime":"2020-01-05T07:57:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-05T17:35:09.000Z","uid":141577,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"7d12530a85a3155bdf4e38badb336457454e53a5","tid":1812011,"uid":141577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T07:57:35.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">歐洲食屍療法</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n//西方駭然於東方夷俗之時，本土卻一度盛行「食人療法」（medicinal cannibalism），早見於古羅馬（例如飲用戰士的血有助治療癲癇症），在 16 世紀至 17 世紀發揚光大，幾乎與草藥一般普遍，德國的劊子手會將死囚器官當藥賣出，英皇查理二世亦曾出價 6,000 鎊收購人頭骨食譜。醫生和病理學家會處方人屍作為藥物，鉅細無遺地交代對象屍體的要求和處理方式，包括種族、年齡、部位、死因甚至暴屍環境，報稱均會影響療效，這種醫學一直到 19 世紀初才見式微。而除人屍外，人屎人尿當時亦被視為「人藥」，能治百病，乃至今日仍有以胎盤入藥的藥方流傳。//<br />\n<br />\n唔知將呢個天然療法傳去中國會點呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d79a923650229c16ec45350e49b4c82a9fcebd8e","tid":1812011,"uid":2419,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T08:14:11.000Z","msg":"北京食屍鬼"},{"pid":"0da215bb2a672de866a1cf9c9606b7e20c05e350","tid":1812011,"uid":227929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T08:15:40.000Z","msg":"結果嚟多劑脘病毒變種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />..."},{"pid":"ebc1ef3c2f97763d0decdf9d472d2c6199d8d168","tid":1812011,"uid":265416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d79a923650229c16ec45350e49b4c82a9fcebd8e","tid":1812011,"uid":2419,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T08:14:11.000Z","msg":"北京食屍鬼"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T08:19:06.000Z","msg":"官方組織CCP"},{"pid":"3c54d8225f8c3aa5a11a6540329cf60250f063e9","tid":1812011,"uid":203955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d79a923650229c16ec45350e49b4c82a9fcebd8e","tid":1812011,"uid":2419,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":3